{"tid":2041344,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"【經濟客飯】你信唔信邱騰華？ - 曾國平","createTime":"2020-05-29T07:38:48.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-29T10:05:25.000Z","uid":25558,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"220f34f4ac9918c0a71ca6ff7e05db6aa99159a1","tid":2041344,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-29T07:38:48.000Z","msg":"全文<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.finance.appledaily.com/finance/20200529/AAIGDTHSZJ2WMMYKWXTXSX5DBI/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.finance.appledaily.com%2Ffinance%2F20200529%2FAAIGDTHSZJ2WMMYKWXTXSX5DBI%2F&d=nsl8wma01YyMGEZOa9B33DUBvjVF43IiJLn9vI4Fxnk%3D&h=09d09bee\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.finance.appledaily.com%2Ffinance%2F20200529%2FAAIGDTHSZJ2WMMYKWXTXSX5DBI%2F&h=1d6a209d\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.finance.appledaily.com/finance/20200529/AAIGDTHSZJ2WMMYKWXTXSX5DBI/</a><br />\n<br />\n【經濟客飯】你信唔信邱騰華？ - 曾國平<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://thumbor-prod-ap-ne-1.photo.aws.arc.pub/uhb_ZUfljp-ynyBNnG8hvxCDRHY=/arc-photo-appledaily/ap-ne-1-prod/public/5DCSWKTGM4RWIL6J6OCHIJEWXA.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fthumbor-prod-ap-ne-1.photo.aws.arc.pub%2Fuhb_ZUfljp-ynyBNnG8hvxCDRHY%3D%2Farc-photo-appledaily%2Fap-ne-1-prod%2Fpublic%2F5DCSWKTGM4RWIL6J6OCHIJEWXA.jpg&h=f5588e4c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n邱騰華早前接受外媒訪問時霸氣指出，美國根本沒有單方面給予香港優惠待遇，香港自由港的地位並不是任何人的禮物。 資料圖片<br />\n<br />\n昨日熱門話題，肯定是美國國務卿蓬佩奧宣佈將會向國會報告，香港不再擁有自治。<br />\n<br />\n碰巧，差不多時間，特區政府發了一篇新聞稿，回應美國全國商會有關。。。。。。。。。。國向香港出口貨物和服務，以及香港在美國的直接投資，在美國創造逾21萬個工作職位。」<br />\n<br />\n我一年多以前做過簡單的推算，21萬個工作職位只佔美國勞動人口極低比例，相比之下，香港從事與美國有關的物流貿易行業比例大得多。再者，這一筆順差好一部份來自轉口，美國放棄香港，不代表這些生意就此消失。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n商務及經濟發展局局長邱騰華早前接受外媒訪問時更有霸氣，指美國根本沒有單方面給予香港優惠待遇，香港自由港的地位並不是任何人的禮物。這些答案好像很動聽，但根本是偷換概念的語言藝術，情況就如你去飲茶，經理跟你相熟不收加一茶芥，兼給你一張好枱，你不把這些當作甚麼優惠，理解成經理對其他客人特別差而已。<br />\n<br />\n曾國平<br />\n美國維珍尼亞理工大學經濟系副教授<br />\n<a href=\"http://fb.com/economics3.0/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ffb.com%2Feconomics3.0%2F&d=nsl8wma01YyMGEZOa9B33DUBvjVF43IiJLn9vI4Fxnk%3D&h=6fd890d6\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://fb.com/economics3.0/</a><br />\n本欄逢周五刊出"},{"pid":"9350a50b74db32e76bd243af24f83764248572ff","tid":2041344,"uid":3149,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-29T09:59:59.000Z","msg":"Push <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0c1d22cca46a529cc855e0d563ff9f8eb5186c57","tid":2041344,"uid":82640,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-29T10:03:23.000Z","msg":"邱騰華，GBS，JP<br />\n香港大學、牛津大學、哈佛大學<br />\n<br />\n然後淨係識戰狼式外交"},{"pid":"02694a7ecf975048e114d9d5619029cd97f6e97a","tid":2041344,"uid":343431,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-29T10:05:25.000Z","msg":"美帝一個covid 19都冇左三千萬份工<br />\n講經濟利益<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}